Text: TXU LSP Friday Holiday Revisedpst TXU LSP observes a holiday on Friday Mar Noms for April firstofthemonth business are due Wednesday Mar at PM Noms for Gas Day Friday Mar through Gas Day Monday Apr are due Thursday Mar at AM fyi Monthly nomination deadlines are posted on our website at wwwtxulspcom Please call your representative if there are any questions

TXU LSP Open Seasonpst TXU Lone Star Pipeline TXU LSP is offering an Open Season for producers developers shippers and marketers who do business in the Ft Worth Basin of the TXU LSP system Descriptions and forms for the Open Season may be found on TXU LSPs web site at usourbuspipelinenoticesmaintasp OR Go to the TXU LSP website at wwwtxulspcom and click on Notices Maintenance For contact information please see the Open Season documents
